DISCLAIMER FOR HACKATHON PROTOTYPE

This software is a proof-of-concept prototype developed for the NHAI 6th 
Innovation Hackathon. While designed to demonstrate AI/ML applications in 
road safety, it should not be used for real-world infrastructure decisions 
without:

1. Validation against handheld retroreflectometer ground truth data
2. Testing on a representative sample of Indian highway conditions
3. Integration with existing NHAI quality assurance procedures
4. Approval from appropriate NHAI authorities

The calibration model is based on typical road conditions and may require 
fine-tuning for specific geographical regions or seasons.

